      "content": "hey so i was just cleaning my ears with a qtip and i heard this loud pop in my left ear. now it just feels completely blocked and i cant hear anything out of it. it's probably just some wax or tinnitus or something right? i'm in oslo and dont really wanna go to the doctor at this hour unless its like an emergency",
