      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what u mean but i'm just really trying to avoid the hospital thing lol. i looked up some stuff online and people say sudden deafness can sometimes just be a temporary pressure thing or even just tinnitus if there's ringing. if i just wait a day or two and use some warm compress, is there any reason i should be worried? it's not like i'm in agony or anything.",
